 live bus tracking:   tweet  to my twitter handle @iitk_bus  & you will get next 3 bus timings  form  your busstop/place of tweetting to the destination 

i.e @iitk_bus <bus_No> form XYZ to <destination>

OR 
@iitkbus <bus_No>  to <destination>
 
or 
@iitk_bus <destination>  (this works when  geo Location service of tweeter account is on)



Tweet automation: 1000 positive tweets per days for particular. it reads all tweets to a #tag and analyses it  if its positive then tweets it otherwise not . SO u can tweet 1000 tweets/days  250-per 4hrs interval 
